e by mixing <b>1 part<b> red food colouring to <b>2 parts<b> yellow food colouring. Adjust intensity of colour as desired.","The required time to whip cream depends on the temperature, fat content and quality of the cream. Take care not to overwhip or the cream will turn into butter. Watch carefully through the hole in the mixing bowl lid and listen for change in the mixing sound. Approximate whipping time is <b>1-2 minutes.<b>","If preferred, cling film could be replaced with lightly oiled baking paper.","Garnish Candy Corn Pudding with Halloween sprinkles, candy corn or candy pumpkins."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","50m","8 portions"]}